\begin_inset Formula $A=\begin{bmatrix}0 & 0\\
0 & 1
\end{bmatrix}$
\end_inset

 and 
\begin_inset Formula $C=\{(x,\mu)|x>0,\mu\geq0,\mu\geq\frac{1}{x}\}$
