 (an epigraph on strictly positive x).
 Notice that C is convex (because 
\begin_inset Formula $f(x)=\frac{1}{x}$
\end_inset

 is convex on 
\begin_inset Formula $x>0$
\end_inset

) and closed.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
Notice that, for some point 
