\begin_inset Formula $\{c_{n}\}\subseteq C$
\end_inset

 s.t.
 
\begin_inset Formula $Ac_{n}=x_{n}$
\end_inset

.
 Because C is compact, we can choose some subsequence of 
\begin_inset Formula $\{c_{n}\}$
\end_inset

 s.t.
